# use \[ and \] to contain the sequence
# actually \\[  AND  \] - bash bug due to color and line wrapping issues
# http://www.rapidtables.com/web/color/RGB_Color.htm
# escape codes -> \e[ or \x1b[ or \033[
# [SGR Code; 2; Reg; Green; Bluem]
# 0  - reset
# 1  - bold
# 2  - dim
# 3  - italic
# 4  - underline
# 7  - invert
# 38 - foreground
# 48 - background

